            "description": "<h2 class=\"text-center font-bebas text-2xl lg:text-4xl\">☀️Summer Sale – 20–40% Off Everything☀️</h2>\n<br>\n\n<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\nThe OddBalls Summer Sale is officially on, with 20–40% off everything sitewide. Whether you're packing for a holiday, refreshing your everyday essentials, or shopping ahead for back-to-work comfort, now’s the perfect time to stock up on our best-selling underwear, swimwear, and accessories — all at discounted prices.\n\n</p> <br> \n<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\n\nOur core underwear collection is included in the sale, with major savings across our most popular styles. Shop <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/him-individuals\" class=\"link\">men’s boxers</a> in colourful prints, breathable <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/bamboo-boxer-shorts\" class=\"link\"> bamboo boxers</a>  for all-day comfort, and relaxed <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/mens-loose-fit-boxers\" class=\"link\">loose-fit cotton boxers</a> that are perfect for warmer days. For women, you’ll find classic <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/mens-loose-fit-boxers\" class=\"link\">boxer short styles</a>, <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/her-individuals\" class=\"link\">briefs</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/ladies-thongs\" class=\"link\">thongs</a> in our signature seasonal designs. If you're looking to buy in bulk or save even more, don’t miss our exclusive summer sale underwear bundles — multi-packs featuring a mix of bestsellers and limited-edition summer prints, only available while stocks last.\n\n</p> <br> \n<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\n\nIf you're off to the beach or chilling poolside, our <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/swimming-shorts\" class=\"link\">men’s swim shorts</a> are also included in the sale. Choose from <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/mens-swim-shorts-with-compression-liner\" class=\"link\">compression-lined</a> styles for added support or our  <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/mens-classic-swim-shorts\" class=\"link\">classic swim shorts</a> made with breathable, quick-drying fabric. Each pair is finished with practical features like mesh or compression linings, adjustable drawstring waists, and side pockets — designed for everything from active swims to bathing in the sun.\n\n</p> <br> \n<p class=\"text-md lg:text-lg\">\n\nNo summer fit is complete without accessories, and our <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/quick-dry-towels\" class=\"link\">quick-dry travel towels</a> and <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/cotton-towel\" class=\"link\">oversized beach towels</a> are made for hot days and spontaneous swims. You’ll also find lightweight <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/sports-shorts\" class=\"link\">gym shorts</a>, <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/training-tops\" class=\"link\">training tops</a> and supportive <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/socks/style-sports\" class=\"link\">sports socks</a> in our <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/mens-sportswear\" class=\"link\">men’s activewear range</a> — ideal for pre-beach workouts or travel days on the move. As an extra treat, we’re offering a <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/free-gift\" class=\"link\">free gift</a> when you spend over £40. Choose from summer essentials like <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/wash-bags\" class=\"link\">wash bags</a>, <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/picnic-blankets\" class=\"link\">picnic blankets</a> or OddBalls <a href=\"https://www.myoddballs.com/collections/sunglasses\" class=\"link\">sunglasses</a> — all perfect accessories for your next getaway. Stock is limited and popular styles are already moving fast. Now’s the time to take advantage of the OddBalls Summer Sale.\n\n</p>",
